ons to demonstrate that 1-bit\nprecoding enables reliable and high-rate downlink data transmission in\npractical systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Feb 2017 19:36:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 20:24:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-09"}
