me aspects of neutrino-driven explosion mechanism. These\nnew comparisons further suggest that the JFM plays a major role in exploding\nmassive stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Feb 2017 19:58:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2017 05:45:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 Jul 2017 16:38:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-08"}
